平面的向量 $\\vec{d} \\in A$ ，满足 $|\\vec{c}-\\vec{d}|=0.5$ (2)对任意 $\\vec{c} \\in A$ ，存在该平面向量 $\\vec{d} \\notin A$ ，满足 $|\\vec{c}-\\vec{d}|=0.5$则下面判断正确的为（） \n    - A.(1)正确，(2)错误 B.(1)错误，(2)正确 C.(1)正确，(2)正确 D.(1)错误，(2)错误\n- > 17 如图， $P$ 为圆锥顶点， $O$ 为底面中心， $A, B, C$ 均在底面圆周上，且 $\\triangle A B C$ 为等边三角形。 ![","target":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/xjhmnDvkx-zAxKZeGuLxooKIeUiusFXewg5ZgcGk9SGmdQRXLegDqYiHe0W5NU2mi0cbi2LDCjZqqm5Ak26uaCfI3rxyZIvfXbcQfwjZl3r0l3CB3_tXLgIHjmoE_gz-.jpeg","line":12}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1hdpw0u","at":1769676328602}},"smart_blocks:RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/2024届24杨浦二模【学生版】试卷.md#": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.07643942,-0.01986656,0.06059278,-0.02779598,-0.02020754,0.00310732,-0.05917174,-0.02105406,0.02814862,-0.01974873,0.02275071,-0.0812128,0.08528196,-0.02433707,0.01274755,0.00418709,-0.01233834,-0.03130565,-0.07344997,0.01438543,0.09695049,-0.04845481,0.01594618,-0.08897442,0.03582177,0.03671347,0.02659176,-0.02450564,0.00658908,-0.20067313,-0.02167783,0.04411373,-0.00591995,0.02236688,0.02160596,-0.0688139,-0.05237597,0.03287069,-0.01169151,0.06341144,0.01483411,0.07715442,0.04394207,-0.01011008,-0.00581784,-0.10444226,-0.0831298,-0.00528283,0.02076771,-0.01312055,-0.01098451,0.01385086,0.01657282,0.06402697,0.00086474,0.0267074,0.03901546,-0.01435443,0.02758222,0.06429609,0.0500984,0.00594239,-0.21793965,0.03096188,0.0221342,0.00115126,-0.03483763,-0.03793847,-0.01199197,0.06591918,-0.03841949,-0.01172803,-0.056318,0.01927598,-0.02269837,0.02434076,0.00515341,-0.06478798,-0.0566316,0.00259924,-0.05026243,0.04379088,-0.04359741,0.00120236,0.00665696,0.01277787,-0.00612257,-0.04658684,0.02065204,0.00385894,-0.02746926,-0.01160966,-0.03062123,0.01246646,-0.04561559,-0.0184467,0.04471174,0.04960994,-0.03923473,0.06741231,-0.0055279,0.02828376,-0.04518091,-0.05354348,-0.00050131,0.00647725,-0.04082498,-0.05549578,-0.0334515,-0.01286067,-0.